      "title": "Notification of power outage",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The current 3-hour power cut will be enforced tomorrow (26) due to the sudden collapse of Nuraicholai Lakvijaya coal plant and shortage of fuel for power generation, the Public Utilities Commission said today (25) afternoon.",
        "According to this, 20 zones from 'A' to 'W' will be cut off for 1 hour 40 minutes during the day and 2 hours 20 minutes at night, the Public Utilities Commission said."
